target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FORTUNE_TASK_UNLOCK_1<tab>Ваш слуга набрался достаточно опыта для того, чтобы отправляться в <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>быстрые исследования<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FORTUNE_TASK_UNLOCK_2<tab>Select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>assign venture<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu to proceed.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FORTUNE_TASK_UNLOCK_2<tab>Select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>assign venture<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu to proceed.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_INTRO_1<tab>You can now send your retainers afield on procurement expeditions known as <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>ventures<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_INTRO_1<tab>You can now send your retainers afield on procurement expeditions known as <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>ventures<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_INTRO_2<tab>Before you can do so, however, you must first assign them a class.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_INTRO_2<tab>Before you can do so, however, you must first assign them a class.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_INTRO_3<tab>After summoning a retainer, select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>assign retainer class<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu to begin.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_INTRO_3<tab>After summoning a retainer, select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>assign retainer class<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu to begin.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_CLASS_1<tab>Your retainer cannot undertake ventures until you assign his or her class.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_CLASS_1<tab>Your retainer cannot undertake ventures until you assign his or her class.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_CLASS_2<tab>This can be any one class, with the exception of those of the Disciples of the Hand.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_CLASS_2<tab>This can be any one class, with the exception of those of the Disciples of the Hand.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_CLASS_3<tab>Your retainer's class determines which ventures he or she can embark upon.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_CLASS_3<tab>Your retainer's class determines which ventures he or she can embark upon.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_CLASS_4<tab>Please be advised that you cannot assign your retainer a class you have not yet unlocked.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_CLASS_4<tab>Please be advised that you cannot assign your retainer a class you have not yet unlocked.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_SECOND_CLASS_2<tab>Please be advised that your retainer must be equipped with a main arm in order to undertake ventures.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_SECOND_CLASS_2<tab>Please be advised that your retainer must be equipped with a main arm in order to undertake ventures.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_CLASS_RESET_1<tab>If you wish to assign your retainer a different class, you must first reset his or her current class.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_CLASS_RESET_1<tab>If you wish to assign your retainer a different class, you must first reset his or her current class.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_CLASS_RESET_2<tab>If necessary, recall your retainer and remove all gear to proceed.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_CLASS_RESET_2<tab>If necessary, recall your retainer and remove all gear to proceed.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_EQUIP_1<tab>You can equip any item in your inventory or Armoury Chest to your retainer, so long as he or she meets the requirements.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_EQUIP_1<tab>You can equip any item in your inventory or Armoury Chest to your retainer, so long as he or she meets the requirements.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_EQUIP_2<tab>Equip a main arm to your retainer to proceed.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_EQUIP_2<tab>Equip a main arm to your retainer to proceed.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FIRST_WEAPON_1<tab>You have equipped a main arm to <var 29 EA02 /var>!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FIRST_WEAPON_1<tab>You have equipped a main arm to <var 29 EA02 /var>!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FIRST_WEAPON_2<tab>Your retainer is now duly prepared to undertake ventures.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FIRST_WEAPON_2<tab>Your retainer is now duly prepared to undertake ventures.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FIRST_WEAPON_3<tab>Select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>assign venture<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu to proceed.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FIRST_WEAPON_3<tab>Select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>assign venture<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu to proceed.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_CLASS_EXPLAIN_START<tab>As you may recall, the ventures your retainer can undertake are determined by his or her class.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_CLASS_EXPLAIN_START<tab>As you may recall, the ventures your retainer can undertake are determined by his or her class.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_VENTURES_1<tab>There are two main types of ventures which you can assign your retainer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_VENTURES_1<tab>There are two main types of ventures which you can assign your retainer.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_VENTURES_2<tab>Hunting, Mining, Botany, and Fishing constitute one type, in which you specify an item for your retainer to procure.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_VENTURES_2<tab>Hunting, Mining, Botany, and Fishing constitute one type, in which you specify an item for your retainer to procure.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_VENTURES_3<tab>Exploration ventures constitute the second type, in which your retainer will scour the terrain of your choosing for (hopefully) precious items.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_VENTURES_3<tab>Exploration ventures constitute the second type, in which your retainer will scour the terrain of your choosing for (hopefully) precious items.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_VENTURES_4<tab>However, your retainer will not undertake a venture without first receiving due compensation.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_VENTURES_4<tab>However, your retainer will not undertake a venture without first receiving due compensation.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_VENTURES_5<tab>Assigning a venture requires a payment in a unique currency of the same name─<var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>ventures<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_VENTURES_5<tab>Assigning a venture requires a payment in a unique currency of the same name─<var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>ventures<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_VENTURES_6<tab>Ventures can be acquired through a variety of methods such as exchanging company seals, fulfilling leve objectives, and completing tribal quests.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_VENTURES_6<tab>Ventures can be acquired through a variety of methods such as exchanging company seals, fulfilling leve objectives, and completing tribal quests.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_VENTURE_1<tab>You have assigned <var 29 EA02 /var> a venture!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_VENTURE_1<tab>You have assigned <var 29 EA02 /var> a venture!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_VENTURE_2<tab>To confirm the time remaining until a venture is complete, select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Timers<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> under Duty from the <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>main menu<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, and select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Ventures<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_VENTURE_2<tab>To confirm the time remaining until a venture is complete, select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Timers<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> under Duty from the <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>main menu<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, and select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Ventures<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_VENTURE_3<tab>You can also confirm the time remaining by selecting <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>view venture report<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_VENTURE_3<tab>You can also confirm the time remaining by selecting <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>view venture report<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_VENTURE_4<tab>Should you wish to cancel the venture and recall your retainer, you may do so when viewing the venture report.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_VENTURE_4<tab>Should you wish to cancel the venture and recall your retainer, you may do so when viewing the venture report.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_VENTURE_5<tab>However, please be advised that this is not necessary unless you wish to assign a different venture to your retainer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_VENTURE_5<tab>However, please be advised that this is not necessary unless you wish to assign a different venture to your retainer.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_VENTURE_6<tab>Even with a venture in progress, you can still entrust or withdraw items and gil, or sell items on the market.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_VENTURE_6<tab>Even with a venture in progress, you can still entrust or withdraw items and gil, or sell items on the market.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_COMPLETED_1<tab><var 29 EA02 /var> has completed a venture!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_COMPLETED_1<tab><var 29 EA02 /var> has completed a venture!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_COMPLETED_2<tab>To claim the fruits of your retainer's labor, select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>view venture report<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_FIRST_COMPLETED_2<tab>To claim the fruits of your retainer's labor, select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>view venture report<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_1<tab><var 29 EA02 /var> has gained experience for completing a venture!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_1<tab><var 29 EA02 /var> has gained experience for completing a venture!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_2<tab>Like you, your retainer can gain experience and levels.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_2<tab>Like you, your retainer can gain experience and levels.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_3<tab>This, in turn, will allow your retainer to undertake a wider variety of ventures, yielding more desirable items.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_3<tab>This, in turn, will allow your retainer to undertake a wider variety of ventures, yielding more desirable items.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_4<tab>Moreover, equipping additional gear to your retainer will increase both the quantity and quality of the items procured.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_4<tab>Moreover, equipping additional gear to your retainer will increase both the quantity and quality of the items procured.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_1<tab>Quick exploration ventures are brief assignments in which you dispatch your retainer without instruction.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_1<tab>Quick exploration ventures are brief assignments in which you dispatch your retainer without instruction.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_2<tab>The items your retainer procures on these ventures can range from worthless to priceless.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_2<tab>The items your retainer procures on these ventures can range from worthless to priceless.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_3<tab>Moreover, the experience your retainer receives for completing a quick exploration venture is determined by their level.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_3<tab>Moreover, the experience your retainer receives for completing a quick exploration venture is determined by their level.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_4<tab>Although it is impossible to predict the results of these ventures, the potential benefits should not be underestimated.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_4<tab>Although it is impossible to predict the results of these ventures, the potential benefits should not be underestimated.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_MIRAGEPRISM_1<tab>Glamours can be applied to gear equipped by or in the possession of your retainers.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_MIRAGEPRISM_1<tab>Можно применить гламуры к предметам, надетым или в находящимся в инвентаре слуги.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_MIRAGEPRISM_2<tab>Moreover, gear equipped by or in the possession of your retainers can be used to apply glamours to your equipped gear, or gear in your inventory.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_MIRAGEPRISM_2<tab>Moreover, gear equipped by or in the possession of your retainers can be used to apply glamours to your equipped gear, or gear in your inventory.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_MIRAGEPRISM_3<tab>Please note a glamour prism is required for each piece of gear you wish to glamour.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_MIRAGEPRISM_3<tab>Please note a glamour prism is required for each piece of gear you wish to glamour.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_EQUIPPAINT_1<tab>Dyes can be used to change the color of any gear equipped by or in the possession of your retainers.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ABOUT_EQUIPPAINT_1<tab>Dyes can be used to change the color of any gear equipped by or in the possession of your retainers.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have come, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have come, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Nothin' fer ye to worry about.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Nothin' fer ye to worry about.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>You summoned?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>You summoned?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Yes? <sigh> I hope this doesn't take long...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Yes? <sigh> I hope this doesn't take long...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You wish to see how a master handles a bazaar?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You wish to see how a master handles a bazaar?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Hello, hello! You called?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Hello, hello! You called?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>At your service, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>At your service, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>What's it to be this time, love?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>What's it to be this time, love?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>What would you ask?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>What would you ask?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I'm so sorry to keep you waiting, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. So very, very sorry.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I'm so sorry to keep you waiting, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. So very, very sorry.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Quickly now, I've places to be.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Quickly now, I've places to be.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Well, if it ain't my favorite client! Always a pleasure, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Well, if it ain't my favorite client! Always a pleasure, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Yes, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>? What is your bidding?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Yes, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>? What is your bidding?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>What's on the agenda, chief? Deprivin' saps o' their hard-earned gil?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>What's on the agenda, chief? Deprivin' saps o' their hard-earned gil?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I have come. You may proceed.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I have come. You may proceed.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Oh, hello there. To what do I owe the pleasure?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Oh, hello there. To what do I owe the pleasure?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I am come to conduct business, and only business.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I am come to conduct business, and only business.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You look to be in good health, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. How may I assist you this fine <var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((eve)) ((morn)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((day)) ((eve)) /var>)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You look to be in good health, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. How may I assist you this fine <var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((eve)) ((morn)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((day)) ((eve)) /var>)) /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>What is it you would have me do, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>What is it you would have me do, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Usually, it's me doin' the summons and others doin' the waitin'.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Usually, it's me doin' the summons and others doin' the waitin'.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Is there something that I can help you with?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Is there something that I can help you with?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Oh, why must you summon me at a time like this...?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Oh, why must you summon me at a time like this...?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I'm sure there is a perfectly good explanation for this summons.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I'm sure there is a perfectly good explanation for this summons.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>You know, I thought you might be along to summon me. You may rest assured that I am ready and eager to serve.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>You know, I thought you might be along to summon me. You may rest assured that I am ready and eager to serve.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Hail to thee, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Your humble servant has heard your summons.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Hail to thee, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Your humble servant has heard your summons.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Greetin's and salutations, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>. Pray speak yer desires, an' I'll do me damndest to see 'em done.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Greetin's and salutations, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>. Pray speak yer desires, an' I'll do me damndest to see 'em done.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I was wondering when you'd get around to calling me.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I was wondering when you'd get around to calling me.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Mind if we keep this brief? I've got a pretty little thing that's waitin' for me.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Mind if we keep this brief? I've got a pretty little thing that's waitin' for me.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>What?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>What?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm here, I'm here!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm here, I'm here!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Here I am, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>, as per your request.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Here I am, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>, as per your request.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>'Ello, dearie. What's on the docket?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>'Ello, dearie. What's on the docket?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I never miss a chance to line these pockets.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I never miss a chance to line these pockets.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, this is unexpected! What'll it be?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, this is unexpected! What'll it be?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>What is it now?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>What is it now?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Here I aaaaaam!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Here I aaaaaam!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>How may I be of serrrvice, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>How may I be of serrrvice, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>It's a war out there, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>. You have no idea.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>It's a war out there, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>. You have no idea.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Business or pleasure?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Business or pleasure?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I presume you did not summon me solely for the pleasure of my company.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I presume you did not summon me solely for the pleasure of my company.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Just the <var 08 E905 ((fair maiden)) ((handsome fellow)) /var> I was hoping to see! Tell me your heart's desire.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Just the <var 08 E905 ((fair maiden)) ((handsome fellow)) /var> I was hoping to see! Tell me your heart's desire.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I hope your catcall is not one of disapproval.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I hope your catcall is not one of disapproval.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye rang, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye rang, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>A cat's ears do not miss much―least of all a summons.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>A cat's ears do not miss much―least of all a summons.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Curiosity called the cat. What do you have for me today?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Curiosity called the cat. What do you have for me today?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Ready when you are.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Ready when you are.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I was just thinking of you!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I was just thinking of you!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>What need have you of me today, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>What need have you of me today, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! Ye got work needs gettin' done? Just point me in the right bloody direction.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! Ye got work needs gettin' done? Just point me in the right bloody direction.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I've come. What is it?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I've come. What is it?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Hey there─hic─<var 08 E905 ((missy)) ((mate)) /var>! Care to join me fer a pint?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Hey there─hic─<var 08 E905 ((missy)) ((mate)) /var>! Care to join me fer a pint?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Couldn't come no quicker. Where's the work?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Couldn't come no quicker. Where's the work?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I came runnin' soon as I heard the bell! Ye need somethin', chief?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I came runnin' soon as I heard the bell! Ye need somethin', chief?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I am at your disposal, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I am at your disposal, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye got somethin' fer me, cap'n?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye got somethin' fer me, cap'n?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Go ahead, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Go ahead, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Let's keep this short and sweet, shall we?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Let's keep this short and sweet, shall we?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>This wouldn't be necessary if you entrusted your financial affairs to me.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>This wouldn't be necessary if you entrusted your financial affairs to me.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>So─sellin', buyin', drinkin', whorin'? What's it to be today?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>So─sellin', buyin', drinkin', whorin'? What's it to be today?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Greetings, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. How may I be of service?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Greetings, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. How may I be of service?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>What'll it be, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((mate)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>What'll it be, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((mate)) /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>State your business.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>State your business.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>And how does this wonderful <var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((evening)) ((day)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((day)) ((evening)) /var>)) /var> find you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>And how does this wonderful <var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((evening)) ((day)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((day)) ((evening)) /var>)) /var> find you?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Well... Here I am...<var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Well... Here I am...<var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>We work the market stalls,♪
And our uniforms are pretty;♪
We are sober men and true,♪
And attentive to our duties!♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>We work the market stalls,♪
And our uniforms are pretty;♪
We are sober men and true,♪
And attentive to our duties!♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((My lady)) ((My lord)) /var>. What would you ask of me?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((My lady)) ((My lord)) /var>. What would you ask of me?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>So. We doing this?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>So. We doing this?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Yes?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Yes?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Hey, it's...it's you! Hello again, you!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Hey, it's...it's you! Hello again, you!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I-It's not like I want to sell your items or anything.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I-It's not like I want to sell your items or anything.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>What do you have for me? Come on, come on! Don't be shy!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>What do you have for me? Come on, come on! Don't be shy!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>You rang, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>You rang, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>I trust this will be worth my while.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>I trust this will be worth my while.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>What<var 1A 01 /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>What<var 1A 01 /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Whatever you need, leave it to me! I have my methods.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Whatever you need, leave it to me! I have my methods.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Gahaha! If it isn't my favorite <var 08 E905 ((mistress)) ((master)) /var>!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Gahaha! If it isn't my favorite <var 08 E905 ((mistress)) ((master)) /var>!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>It is I, your most loyal and capable retainer!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>It is I, your most loyal and capable retainer!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>What will it be, love?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>What will it be, love?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Your orders! I would hear them at once!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Your orders! I would hear them at once!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>If there is something you would ask of me, then ask it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>If there is something you would ask of me, then ask it.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Yes...? Is there something you─<yawn>─need?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Yes...? Is there something you─<yawn>─need?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>A task for me? I hope it's something fun!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>A task for me? I hope it's something fun!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I am here to do your every bidding, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>! Ask of me anything at all!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I am here to do your every bidding, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>! Ask of me anything at all!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have been awaiting your summons, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. What would you have of me this fine <var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((evening)) ((morning)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((day)) ((evening)) /var>)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have been awaiting your summons, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. What would you have of me this fine <var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((evening)) ((morning)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((day)) ((evening)) /var>)) /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>What can I do for ye, yer <var 08 E905 ((ladyship)) ((lordship)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>What can I do for ye, yer <var 08 E905 ((ladyship)) ((lordship)) /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>You called, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>...?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>You called, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>...?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>You─hic─rang?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>You─hic─rang?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Need my assistance, do you? Let's make this quick, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Need my assistance, do you? Let's make this quick, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You have my ear, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>. Both of them, in fact!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You have my ear, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>. Both of them, in fact!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If that is all, I will take my leave now, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If that is all, I will take my leave now, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Take care o' yerself, hear?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Take care o' yerself, hear?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Until we next meet.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Until we next meet.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, it's about time. Good-bye.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, it's about time. Good-bye.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I believe thanks are in order.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I believe thanks are in order.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm off, then!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm off, then!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>With your leave, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>With your leave, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Don't you worry 'bout a thing. I got this.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Don't you worry 'bout a thing. I got this.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Farewell, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Farewell, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>If there is nothing else, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, I'll be going now.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>If there is nothing else, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, I'll be going now.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Is that all? Very well, until next time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Is that all? Very well, until next time.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Oh, will that be all today? Very well, but promise me you'll come back soon!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Oh, will that be all today? Very well, but promise me you'll come back soon!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>As always, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, it has been an honor and a privilege.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>As always, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, it has been an honor and a privilege.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>You can count on me, chief─I know how to get things done.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>You can count on me, chief─I know how to get things done.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Don't be a stranger.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Don't be a stranger.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I swear it shall be done. Eventually.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I swear it shall be done. Eventually.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>As you wish.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>As you wish.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Capital! I shall carry out your orders forthwith.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Capital! I shall carry out your orders forthwith.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I humbly await your next summons, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I humbly await your next summons, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Don't leave me alone for too long, hear?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Don't leave me alone for too long, hear?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Always a pleasure.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Always a pleasure.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>That will be all, yes? Then if you would excuse me...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>That will be all, yes? Then if you would excuse me...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I believe that concludes our dealings for now.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I believe that concludes our dealings for now.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Are you certain you don't desire anything else? Anything at all? Very well, I shall take my leave.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Are you certain you don't desire anything else? Anything at all? Very well, I shall take my leave.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Your every whim shall be swiftly carried out with due care and consideration.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Your every whim shall be swiftly carried out with due care and consideration.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Shouldn't take more than a moment, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Shouldn't take more than a moment, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I'll be going, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I'll be going, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Thank the gods we're finished. I've got plans to put my hands in places I've never seen...if you know what I mean.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Thank the gods we're finished. I've got plans to put my hands in places I've never seen...if you know what I mean.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Be well.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Be well.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm off, I'm off!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm off, I'm off!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Until we meet again!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Until we meet again!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Blessin's o' the Twelve upon ye.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Blessin's o' the Twelve upon ye.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>May Nald'thal see fit to fatten our pockets!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>May Nald'thal see fit to fatten our pockets!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Very good, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! Your wish is my command, and so forth.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Very good, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! Your wish is my command, and so forth.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You know how to reach me.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You know how to reach me.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Is it time for good-byes already? I'm going to miss you...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Is it time for good-byes already? I'm going to miss you...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Thy will be done.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Thy will be done.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>The markets may be a bleedin' battlefield, but I'm a godsdamned soldier. You can count on me, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>The markets may be a bleedin' battlefield, but I'm a godsdamned soldier. You can count on me, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Why so serrrious? <sigh> So it goes.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Why so serrrious? <sigh> So it goes.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I hardly think that warranted my personal appearance, but what is done is done.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I hardly think that warranted my personal appearance, but what is done is done.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Then I have satisfied your every need? Excellent! I do so take pleasure in servicing my clients.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Then I have satisfied your every need? Excellent! I do so take pleasure in servicing my clients.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Good-bye for now, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Good-bye for now, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Right then, let's get on with it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Right then, let's get on with it!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There is no call for concerrrn.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There is no call for concerrrn.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>When the master's away, the cat will play.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>When the master's away, the cat will play.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Gods, this is tirin'...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Gods, this is tirin'...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>You don't want to be with me anymore? <sniffle>
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>You don't want to be with me anymore? <sniffle>

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall carry out your wishes as instructed, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall carry out your wishes as instructed, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! I'm in yer bazaar, sellin' yer wares!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! I'm in yer bazaar, sellin' yer wares!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I will go now.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I will go now.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Awww, bugger. Reckon I best get to work...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Awww, bugger. Reckon I best get to work...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I don't do good-byes.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I don't do good-byes.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Go and grab yourself some shut-eye, chief. You look terrible!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Go and grab yourself some shut-eye, chief. You look terrible!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Will that be all for today, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>? Understood.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Will that be all for today, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>? Understood.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Aye, aye, cap'n!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Aye, aye, cap'n!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Duly noted.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Duly noted.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Not exactly how I was hopin' to spend my day, but I suppose it can't be helped.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Not exactly how I was hopin' to spend my day, but I suppose it can't be helped.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Ours is not to reason why. Ours is but to do and die.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Ours is not to reason why. Ours is but to do and die.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Ever the consummate professional, I see. Another time, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Ever the consummate professional, I see. Another time, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If there is nothing else, then I shall take my leave.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If there is nothing else, then I shall take my leave.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Is that all? Guess I'll be on my way, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Is that all? Guess I'll be on my way, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Any last requests? Very well. Heh heh heh... Ahem.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Any last requests? Very well. Heh heh heh... Ahem.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Ah, yes, of course. Duty calls!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Ah, yes, of course. Duty calls!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You are finished with me, then?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You are finished with me, then?

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Here today and gone tomorrow;♪
Yes, I know─♪
That is so!♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Here today and gone tomorrow;♪
Yes, I know─♪
That is so!♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>If ever you have need of me, just ring.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>If ever you have need of me, just ring.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Always a pleasure, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Always a pleasure, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Right, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Right, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Finished already? Guess that's that, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Finished already? Guess that's that, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You're leaving already? Fine, then! I-It's not like I wanted you to stay or anything.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You're leaving already? Fine, then! I-It's not like I wanted you to stay or anything.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Very good, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! Very good indeed!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Very good, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! Very good indeed!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Always a pleasure to serve, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Always a pleasure to serve, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Hmph. I hope that next time you will have a more meaningful task for me.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Hmph. I hope that next time you will have a more meaningful task for me.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Good-bye<var 1A 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Good-bye<var 1A 01 /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>And with that, I shall be off. Places to go, people to see.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>And with that, I shall be off. Places to go, people to see.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Bahahaha! Till next time, my friend!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Bahahaha! Till next time, my friend!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Ring for me whenever you please! You know that I will never let you down!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Ring for me whenever you please! You know that I will never let you down!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Must we part so soon?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Must we part so soon?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>And I am off!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>And I am off!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Call on me as you please. If I am so inclined, I will answer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Call on me as you please. If I am so inclined, I will answer.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>That is all, I suppose...? <yawn> Very well...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>That is all, I suppose...? <yawn> Very well...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>That is all? Oh, I was hoping there'd be more...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>That is all? Oh, I was hoping there'd be more...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Is that all you need of me? But I could yet serve you in so many ways!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Is that all you need of me? But I could yet serve you in so many ways!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Do not hesitate to call upon me again. Fare you well in your endeavors, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Do not hesitate to call upon me again. Fare you well in your endeavors, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Just say the word, yer <var 08 E905 ((ladyship)) ((lordship)) /var>, and I'll be here with bells on.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Just say the word, yer <var 08 E905 ((ladyship)) ((lordship)) /var>, and I'll be here with bells on.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>If you have no further need of my services...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>If you have no further need of my services...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I'm off for another glass, then. You know where to find me!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I'm off for another glass, then. You know where to find me!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>What─is that it? Are you <var 1A 02 /var>sure<var 1A 01 /var> you need a retainer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>What─is that it? Are you <var 1A 02 /var>sure<var 1A 01 /var> you need a retainer?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Nothing else? Then I shall be hopping along.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Nothing else? Then I shall be hopping along.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Your bidding will be done, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Your bidding will be done, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Easy now, easy. I'm on it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Easy now, easy. I'm on it.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>And so it begins.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Very well, if I must...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I shall see to things from here.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I shall see to things from here.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Leave it to me!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Leave it to me!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I understand, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I understand, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Hah! I'll be back afore you know it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Hah! I'll be back afore you know it.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>If that is what you would ask of me.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>If that is what you would ask of me.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I'll give it my best, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I'll give it my best, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Your enterprise is in capable hands, I assure you.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Your enterprise is in capable hands, I assure you.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I won't let you down, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I won't let you down, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall not fail you, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall not fail you, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>No need to worry, chief─this is where I shine.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>No need to worry, chief─this is where I shine.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Leave it to me.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Leave it to me.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Whatever you say.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Whatever you say.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Good. I prefer to work alone.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Good. I prefer to work alone.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Ahhh, I do so enjoy the occasional excursion!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Ahhh, I do so enjoy the occasional excursion!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>As you ask, so shall it be done, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>As you ask, so shall it be done, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Work to be done, eh? All right, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Work to be done, eh? All right, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I'll take care of everything.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I'll take care of everything.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>A venture? <var 1A 02 /var>Now<var 1A 01 /var>? Well, if you insist.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>A venture? <var 1A 02 /var>Now<var 1A 01 /var>? Well, if you insist.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I am well aware of how this works.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I am well aware of how this works.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>That sounds like fun! You'll be joining me, yes? <var 1A 02 /var>No<var 1A 01 /var>? Oh.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>That sounds like fun! You'll be joining me, yes? <var 1A 02 /var>No<var 1A 01 /var>? Oh.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>You will not be disappointed, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>You will not be disappointed, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>You got it, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>You got it, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>That's it? All right.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>That's it? All right.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Hope you ain't expectin' me to rush. I wanna take it nice and slow.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Hope you ain't expectin' me to rush. I wanna take it nice and slow.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I think I can manage from here.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll do it, I'll do it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll do it, I'll do it!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>It is an honor to serve you, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>It is an honor to serve you, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Is that all? A triflin' task!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Is that all? A triflin' task!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>If there's profit to be made, I'll make it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>If there's profit to be made, I'll make it.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>My every waking minute will be spent working on your behalf, et cetera.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>My every waking minute will be spent working on your behalf, et cetera.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Fine...for now. But you're asking a bit much, considering what I'm paid.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Fine...for now. But you're asking a bit much, considering what I'm paid.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Time to shine, hee hee!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Excellent decision, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Venturrres are my specialty.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Excellent decision, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Venturrres are my specialty.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>A special solo mission? Hells, why didn't you say so sooner! Of course I'll do it!

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Business. Always business with you. Fine...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Business. Always business with you. Fine...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Leave me to my task, and we shall both be satisfied.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Leave me to my task, and we shall both be satisfied.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You will be most pleased with the result. I guarantee it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You will be most pleased with the result. I guarantee it!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>It shall be done forthwith, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>It shall be done forthwith, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ah, I was in the mood for a jaunt outside!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>You needn't say another worrrd.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>You needn't say another worrrd.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I'll start now, if that's what you want.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I'll start now, if that's what you want.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Not quite <var 1A 02 /var>ad<var 1A 01 /var>venturin', but it's close enough.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Not quite <var 1A 02 /var>ad<var 1A 01 /var>venturin', but it's close enough.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll do anything you say, exactly as you say.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll do anything you say, exactly as you say.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall not keep you waiting overlong, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall not keep you waiting overlong, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! So that's what this is about! I'll handle it!

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Understood.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Nothing─hic─nothing to it!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I can go now, right? Great.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I can go now, right? Great.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I will not be long, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye picked the right woman fer the job, cap'n!

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I see. All right, then.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I see you finally have the good sense to grant me greater autonomy.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Neither rain nor sleet nor ferocious beasts shall keep me from my task.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Oh, I'll get busy. I'll get very busy, indeed.
