source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Very well...if you insist.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Very well...if you insist.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>That certainly sounds interesting! Well, I'd best be on my way!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>That certainly sounds interesting! Well, I'd best be on my way!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>If that is your heart's desire, then so it shall be!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>If that is your heart's desire, then so it shall be!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>As you have commanded, so I will see it done!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>As you have commanded, so I will see it done!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Right ye are, then!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Right ye are, then!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Very good, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Consider it done.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Very good, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Consider it done.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>But of course, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>! I'm not as─hic─unsteady as all that!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>But of course, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>! I'm not as─hic─unsteady as all that!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I'll take care of it. Just as long as you're suitably grateful.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I'll take care of it. Just as long as you're suitably grateful.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll see it done in two shakes of a rabbit's tail!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll see it done in two shakes of a rabbit's tail!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I pray this meets with your satisfaction, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I pray this meets with your satisfaction, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>How's that grab ye?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>How's that grab ye?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Take it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Take it.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Let's not do this again for a while, shall we?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Let's not do this again for a while, shall we?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Do not behave as though you are not impressed.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Do not behave as though you are not impressed.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Not bad, eh?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Not bad, eh?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>May it please you, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>May it please you, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>How do you like me now, love?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>How do you like me now, love?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>It is what it is.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>It is what it is.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>That's the last of it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>That's the last of it.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Of course it was a success. Did you doubt me?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Of course it was a success. Did you doubt me?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I think that went well, don't you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I think that went well, don't you?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It was my pleasure, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It was my pleasure, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>A rousin' success, if I do say so myself.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>A rousin' success, if I do say so myself.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Enough?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Enough?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>It's all yours. Enjoy.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>It's all yours. Enjoy.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I trust you have no complaints? Good.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I trust you have no complaints? Good.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>What I wouldn't give to do this all the time!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>What I wouldn't give to do this all the time!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Does it please you, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Does it please you, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>One day it'll be me givin' the orders.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>One day it'll be me givin' the orders.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Let me know when you want me to handle another.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Let me know when you want me to handle another.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>A thoroughly pedestrian result, I'm afraid. I would understand if you decided not to assign me ventures henceforth.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>A thoroughly pedestrian result, I'm afraid. I would understand if you decided not to assign me ventures henceforth.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>And there you have it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>And there you have it.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I live to serve.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I live to serve.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Your humble servant hopes that you find the fruits of his labor acceptable.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Your humble servant hopes that you find the fruits of his labor acceptable.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Could be better, but could be worse.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Could be better, but could be worse.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Here, as promised.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Here, as promised.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I knew I could satisfy your needs.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I knew I could satisfy your needs.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Here.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Here.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Take it, take it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Take it, take it!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>My only regret is that I could not return sooner.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>My only regret is that I could not return sooner.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Go on, dearie, take it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Go on, dearie, take it!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>'Twas a most profitable venture, I'd say.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>'Twas a most profitable venture, I'd say.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Always a pleasure to serve, and so on and so forth.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Always a pleasure to serve, and so on and so forth.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You're welcome.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You're welcome.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Some of my finest work yet!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Some of my finest work yet!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It is an honor to serrrve, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It is an honor to serrrve, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>I await your orders, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>I await your orders, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Why don't we both take it easy for a while?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Why don't we both take it easy for a while?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>And with that, we can move on to more important matters.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>And with that, we can move on to more important matters.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Was it everything you hoped it would be?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Was it everything you hoped it would be?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Your goods, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Your goods, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Just what ye wanted, am I right?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Just what ye wanted, am I right?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Thank you for your patronage.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Thank you for your patronage.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Can I go now?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Can I go now?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>And that's the end of that chapter.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>And that's the end of that chapter.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I hope you like it...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I hope you like it...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If you require aught else, you need only ask.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If you require aught else, you need only ask.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Here.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Here.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Why don't we toast our success with a pint or two?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Why don't we toast our success with a pint or two?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>If you want, I can undertake another one right now.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>If you want, I can undertake another one right now.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>It's all there, chief. Ye have me word.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>It's all there, chief. Ye have me word.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((Milady)) ((Milord)) /var> is satisfied, I trust?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((Milady)) ((Milord)) /var> is satisfied, I trust?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>A good haul, all in all.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>A good haul, all in all.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>A pleasure as always.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>A pleasure as always.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Hope you're godsdamned happy.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Hope you're godsdamned happy.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You yourself could do no better.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You yourself could do no better.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>That ought to do it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>That ought to do it.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I pray that you are pleased with the result, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I pray that you are pleased with the result, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bet you weren't expecting <var 1A 02 /var>that<var 1A 01 /var> now, were you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bet you weren't expecting <var 1A 02 /var>that<var 1A 01 /var> now, were you?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Ah, for the days when ventures were a gentleman's pursuit...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Ah, for the days when ventures were a gentleman's pursuit...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If you don't mind me saying, I think I did rather well.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If you don't mind me saying, I think I did rather well.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I will be expected to do this again, I gather.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I will be expected to do this again, I gather.

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Can I survive this overbearing,♪
Or live a life of mad despairing,♪
My proffered goods despised, rejected?♪
No, no, it's not to be expected!♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Can I survive this overbearing,♪
Or live a life of mad despairing,♪
My proffered goods despised, rejected?♪
No, no, it's not to be expected!♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I live to serve, <var 08 E905 ((my lady)) ((my lord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I live to serve, <var 08 E905 ((my lady)) ((my lord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>All's well that ends well, wouldn't you say?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>All's well that ends well, wouldn't you say?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There it is.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There it is.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>All acquired in accordance with local laws. <wink> <wink>
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>All acquired in accordance with local laws. <wink> <wink>

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Alright, take yer shite and quit leerin' at me arse.
...What? Ye can't seriously expect me to humor yer fetishes all the time, can ye?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Alright, take yer shite and quit leerin' at me arse.
...What? Ye can't seriously expect me to humor yer fetishes all the time, can ye?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Hardly my finest work, but I'm not ashamed to say I did it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Hardly my finest work, but I'm not ashamed to say I did it.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Only the best for you, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Only the best for you, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>This is what you asked for, yes? So take it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>This is what you asked for, yes? So take it.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Here<var 1A 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Here<var 1A 01 /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Here's what you wanted! And, er...let us focus on the <var 1A 02 /var>what<var 1A 01 /var> and not talk about the <var 1A 02 /var>how<var 1A 01 /var>, yes?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Here's what you wanted! And, er...let us focus on the <var 1A 02 /var>what<var 1A 01 /var> and not talk about the <var 1A 02 /var>how<var 1A 01 /var>, yes?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I trust this meets with your satisfaction, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>? After all, your contented smile is my greatest reward!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I trust this meets with your satisfaction, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>? After all, your contented smile is my greatest reward!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Does that meet with <var 08 E905 ((her ladyship)) ((his lordship)) /var>'s approval? (It bloody better...)

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>No need to thank me, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Fulfilling one's duty is its own reward.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Not bad, eh? In fact, I think we should pop a cork to celebrate!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>This is what you wanted, yes? I told you I'd take care of it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>This is what you wanted, yes? I told you I'd take care of it.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>And there you have it, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>─all wrapped up like a Hatching<var 1F /var>tide gift basket.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>And there you have it, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>─all wrapped up like a Hatching<var 1F /var>tide gift basket.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Do you require aught else, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Do you require aught else, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>What is it?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>What now? I'm busy.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Yes, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Somethin' else, love?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Well? What is it?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>You couldn't have picked a more inconvenient time.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>This better be worth my time.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>What is it, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>? Something urgent?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>You have additional orders, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Tell me you ain't got somethin' else for me, chief!

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>You have interrupted my venture. Proceed.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I'm here now, so...

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You interrupt my task. Why?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Apologies for the delay, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Apologies for the delay, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>!

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((Milady)) ((Milord)) /var> has another task for me?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I'm a little busy, but what is it?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Was there something else?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Was there something else?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Summons? <var 1A 02 /var>Now<var 1A 01 /var>? Well, if you insist.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Summons? <var 1A 02 /var>Now<var 1A 01 /var>? Well, if you insist.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You do know how this works, right? You assign me a venture and then leave me to my task.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You do know how this works, right? You assign me a venture and then leave me to my task.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Missed me, didn't you?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Hail to thee, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Your humble servant has set aside his task and hastened to your side.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Hail to thee, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Your humble servant has set aside his task and hastened to your side.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Why'd ye call me back from me venture, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Why'd ye call me back from me venture, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>This really isn't the best time.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I thought you were going to let me do this my way?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>What!?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>How may I serve you, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Did somethin' 'appen, dearie?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>What's all this, then? Another chance for mischief?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab><yawn> Just so you know, I was busy carrying out your tasks.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>This had better be important.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have rrreturned, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Damn, just when I was startin' to enjoy meself!

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>A cat must be allowed to focus on her task.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>You know I've not finished the venture yet, rrright?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Mind explainin' what this is about?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>You know, you shouldn't summon me when I'm in the middle of a venture!

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Did you require aught else, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! Ye need somethin' else?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I've returned. What is it now?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Yeah? I was just enjoyin' a pint of─hic─uh, venturin'.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I've already got my hands full with this venture, but what is it?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>What else ye need, chief?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I am at <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>'s beck and call.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I am at <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>'s beck and call.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>What'll it be, cap'n?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab><var 08 E905 ((Madam)) ((Sir)) /var>?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Is aught amiss, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Something on your mind, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((mate)) /var>?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I have a life outside of <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>, you know.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Let me tell you, it was absolute chaos out there. Quite frankly, I'm lucky to be alive! But I heard your call, and I knew I had to answer.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Now, before you go jumping to conclusions, I'd just like to─ Oh! What can I do for you?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I-It's not like I was slaving away to make you happy or anything.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>I am here. I don't have to be happy about it.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Well, that was awfully sudden! You truly cannot get enough of me, can you?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I was hoping you would call, love.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Was there something else, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>...?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Yes? This is interfering with <var 1A 02 /var>your<var 1A 01 /var> venture, just so you know.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Right, then. Back to it.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You've got it!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Understood, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Understood, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye still want me to carry out that venture, too, eh? Just checkin'.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye still want me to carry out that venture, too, eh? Just checkin'.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Acknowledged.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Acknowledged.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>'Fore you ask, I've not forgotten about the venture.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>'Fore you ask, I've not forgotten about the venture.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>If you want quality work, then leave me be.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>If you want quality work, then leave me be.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Now then, where was I...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Now then, where was I...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Then if you would excuse me, I should return to my venture.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Then if you would excuse me, I should return to my venture.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Right, then. I ought to be getting back to that thing of yours. “Venture,” was it...?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Right, then. I ought to be getting back to that thing of yours. “Venture,” was it...?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>We shall meet again, old friend. But now I must steal away into the night.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>We shall meet again, old friend. But now I must steal away into the night.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If I don't make it back, I just want you to know... Eh, the hells with it. I'll tell you next time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If I don't make it back, I just want you to know... Eh, the hells with it. I'll tell you next time.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>As you wish...<var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>As you wish...<var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I must wander to and fro;♪
But wherever I may go,♪
I shall never be untrue to thee!♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I must wander to and fro;♪
But wherever I may go,♪
I shall never be untrue to thee!♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((My lady)) ((My lord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((My lady)) ((My lord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I suppose you'll be wanting me to finish that venture too, yes? Right, right. Don't know why I bothered asking...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I suppose you'll be wanting me to finish that venture too, yes? Right, right. Don't know why I bothered asking...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Hmm.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Hmm.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Right, so, if anyone asks, I wasn't here, agreed? Cheers.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Right, so, if anyone asks, I wasn't here, agreed? Cheers.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Go on, then. Go. It's not like I haven't more important things to do or anything.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Go on, then. Go. It's not like I haven't more important things to do or anything.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Hm, hm. You've really nothin' else to ask? If you say so, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Hm, hm. You've really nothin' else to ask? If you say so, then.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I am ever at your beck and call, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I am ever at your beck and call, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Don't expect me to play errand boy for you forever.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Don't expect me to play errand boy for you forever.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Enough<var 1A 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Enough<var 1A 01 /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If there's nothing else, I'll be getting back to...er, what was it again? Oh, yes, the venture!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If there's nothing else, I'll be getting back to...er, what was it again? Oh, yes, the venture!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Gahahaha! Back to work for me!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Gahahaha! Back to work for me!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Are you sure you don't want to spend more time with me? Ah, but I jest!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Are you sure you don't want to spend more time with me? Ah, but I jest!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>If ever you're feeling lonely, I am but a ring of the bell away.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>If ever you're feeling lonely, I am but a ring of the bell away.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I am off! At least until you call me back again...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I am off! At least until you call me back again...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>The road calls me again.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>The road calls me again.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab><yawn> I really could use a nap...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab><yawn> I really could use a nap...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Well, back to the grind! I do hope you appreciate all this!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Well, back to the grind! I do hope you appreciate all this!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>If that is all, I shall return to my task. Ah, the joy of adventure!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>If that is all, I shall return to my task. Ah, the joy of adventure!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Are you certain? If needs be, I can return at a moment's notice!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Are you certain? If needs be, I can return at a moment's notice!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>If that'll be all, I'll get back to that other thing ye asked me to do.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>If that'll be all, I'll get back to that other thing ye asked me to do.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>If you've no further need of me, I shall return to my assigned task.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>If you've no further need of me, I shall return to my assigned task.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I'll head back out, then. Duty first, debauchery second!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I'll head back out, then. Duty first, debauchery second!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Hmph. You're sure that's everything? I'd rather not be running back and forth, if it's all the same to you.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Hmph. You're sure that's everything? I'd rather not be running back and forth, if it's all the same to you.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I really must be on the road again. Pray no harm befalls my soft, furry hide!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I really must be on the road again. Pray no harm befalls my soft, furry hide!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It pleases me to inform you that the venture is complete.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It pleases me to inform you that the venture is complete.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Hey, I finished that venture o' yours.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Hey, I finished that venture o' yours.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>It is done.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>It is done.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, that was exhausting...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, that was exhausting...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Your venture is finished.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Your venture is finished.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Guess what I finished!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Guess what I finished!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>My <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>, the venture you bid me undertake has been finished.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>My <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>, the venture you bid me undertake has been finished.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I've got your goods, by the way. Let me know when you want 'em.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I've got your goods, by the way. Let me know when you want 'em.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I have something for you.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I have something for you.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Thank the gods that's over.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Thank the gods that's over.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>My venture report is ready.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>My venture report is ready.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Good news, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! The venture was a success!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Good news, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! The venture was a success!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((Madam)) ((Sir)) /var>, your venture is complete.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((Madam)) ((Sir)) /var>, your venture is complete.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Got somethin' for you, chief!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Got somethin' for you, chief!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I have come with your goods.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I have come with your goods.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I took care of that venture for you.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I took care of that venture for you.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You wish to hear my report?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You wish to hear my report?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Ahhh, now that was fun!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Ahhh, now that was fun!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I come with good tidings, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I come with good tidings, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>This about the venture? I took care of it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>This about the venture? I took care of it.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There you are! I've brought what you requested.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There you are! I've brought what you requested.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Oh, it's you. I suppose you'll want to hear about the venture.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Oh, it's you. I suppose you'll want to hear about the venture.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Let's get on with it, shall we?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Let's get on with it, shall we?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I've been waiting for your summons.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I've been waiting for your summons.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Hail to thee, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. You shall be pleased to hear that the venture was a success.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Hail to thee, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. You shall be pleased to hear that the venture was a success.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>You want this stuff now or later?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>You want this stuff now or later?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I'm finished.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I'm finished.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Been a long time comin', but the venture's finally finished.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Been a long time comin', but the venture's finally finished.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Whew.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Whew.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I did it, I did it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I did it, I did it!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Does <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var> wish to hear my report?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Does <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var> wish to hear my report?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>'Ello, dearie. I reckon you want your goods?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>'Ello, dearie. I reckon you want your goods?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>My pockets are bursting with your goods!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>My pockets are bursting with your goods!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, this was to be expected. The venture, yes?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, this was to be expected. The venture, yes?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>We should talk about the venture.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>We should talk about the venture.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm baaack!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm baaack!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>My rrreport is rrready, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>My rrreport is rrready, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Mission accomplished, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Mission accomplished, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>May I leave after making my report? No? <sigh>
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>May I leave after making my report? No? <sigh>

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I have prepared a formal report.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I have prepared a formal report.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Am I to deliver my report now, or shall we discuss other matters first?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Am I to deliver my report now, or shall we discuss other matters first?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>This cat has brought you a present, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>This cat has brought you a present, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye want to hear the whole story, or just read the report?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye want to hear the whole story, or just read the report?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>'Twas naught more than a rrroutine task.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>'Twas naught more than a rrroutine task.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I did my very best, just like I said.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I did my very best, just like I said.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Everythin' you need to know is in the report.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Everythin' you need to know is in the report.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I have so much to tell you!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I have so much to tell you!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have brought that which you desire, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have brought that which you desire, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! That venture was an <var 1A 02 /var>ad<var 1A 01 /var>venture, let me tell ye!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! That venture was an <var 1A 02 /var>ad<var 1A 01 /var>venture, let me tell ye!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>The venture is complete.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>The venture is complete.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Venture? What in the seven hells are ye─ Oh, the <var 1A 02 /var>venture<var 1A 01 /var>! Aye, I did that.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Venture? What in the seven hells are ye─ Oh, the <var 1A 02 /var>venture<var 1A 01 /var>! Aye, I did that.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Got a delivery for you. Just say the word.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Got a delivery for you. Just say the word.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Hey, chief! I got what ye asked for!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Hey, chief! I got what ye asked for!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I have what <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var> requested in my possession.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I have what <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var> requested in my possession.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I've got the goods, cap'n!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I've got the goods, cap'n!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Venture complete, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Venture complete, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Took a while, but the venture's done.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Took a while, but the venture's done.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I had a mind to summon <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>, actually.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I had a mind to summon <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>, actually.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>This venturin' business ain't so bad!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>This venturin' business ain't so bad!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It pleases me to inform you that the venture is complete.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It pleases me to inform you that the venture is complete.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Guess what I've got for you! No, really. Guess!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Guess what I've got for you! No, really. Guess!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I renew my objection to that pointless endeavor. Informally now and by affidavit later.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I renew my objection to that pointless endeavor. Informally now and by affidavit later.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>You know, I think I'm starting to get the hang of this.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>You know, I think I'm starting to get the hang of this.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Per your orders, I have completed the venture...<var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Per your orders, I have completed the venture...<var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>For he himself has said it,♪
And it's greatly to his credit,♪
That he is a retainer!♪
He remains a retainer!♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>For he himself has said it,♪
And it's greatly to his credit,♪
That he is a retainer!♪
He remains a retainer!♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I have seen to the venture, <var 08 E905 ((my lady)) ((my lord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I have seen to the venture, <var 08 E905 ((my lady)) ((my lord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Oh, the tales I could tell you about that venture...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Oh, the tales I could tell you about that venture...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I've finished.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I've finished.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Heh, didn't expect him to put up such a─ Oh! Just the <var 08 E905 ((woman)) ((man)) /var> I was hoping to see!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Heh, didn't expect him to put up such a─ Oh! Just the <var 08 E905 ((woman)) ((man)) /var> I was hoping to see!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I-It's not like I risked life and limb to bring you back shiny baubles or anything.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I-It's not like I risked life and limb to bring you back shiny baubles or anything.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Oh, it has been a day such as you wouldn't believe!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Oh, it has been a day such as you wouldn't believe!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Rest assured that I spared no effort in doing your bidding, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Rest assured that I spared no effort in doing your bidding, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>This is all you will get from me. I hope it satisfies you.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>This is all you will get from me. I hope it satisfies you.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Done<var 1A 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Done<var 1A 01 /var>.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I'm back! Now, do you want the good news or the bad news?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I'm back! Now, do you want the good news or the bad news?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Gahahaha! Feast your eyes on this!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Gahahaha! Feast your eyes on this!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Guess who's returned with a tale to tell? Why, <var 1A 02 /var>me<var 1A 01 /var>, of course!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Guess who's returned with a tale to tell? Why, <var 1A 02 /var>me<var 1A 01 /var>, of course!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I have returned, love. And do I have a tale to tell...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I have returned, love. And do I have a tale to tell...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Hah! Now <var 1A 02 /var>that<var 1A 01 /var> was a venture for the ages!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Hah! Now <var 1A 02 /var>that<var 1A 01 /var> was a venture for the ages!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There are places I would rather be, yet here I am. Be grateful.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There are places I would rather be, yet here I am. Be grateful.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab><yawn> Oh...that's right. I had something to tell you.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab><yawn> Oh...that's right. I had something to tell you.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I've returned! Come now, are you not happy to see me?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I've returned! Come now, are you not happy to see me?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I could scarcely wait to return to your side, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I could scarcely wait to return to your side, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I am returned! And I have come bearing a gift.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I am returned! And I have come bearing a gift.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>About damn time! My ears were twitching summat fierce listening out for that bell...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>About damn time! My ears were twitching summat fierce listening out for that bell...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I believe this concludes your venture, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I believe this concludes your venture, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I have returned, and gods have I worked up a thirst! Oh, and this is for you!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I have returned, and gods have I worked up a thirst! Oh, and this is for you!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I did what you asked. You'll be wanting my full report, then?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I did what you asked. You'll be wanting my full report, then?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Wait until you see the goods I got my paws on!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Wait until you see the goods I got my paws on!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_PIXIE_1<tab>Oh, my adorable sapling! You have need of <var 29 EA02 /var>, yes? But sing the word, and let your beautiful branch do what only they can.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_PIXIE_1<tab>Oh, my adorable sapling! You have need of <var 29 EA02 /var>, yes? But sing the word, and let your beautiful branch do what only they can.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_PIXIE_1<tab>A whispered word, and off goes <var 29 EA02 /var> on a grand adventure! What wonders await at journey's end?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_PIXIE_1<tab>A whispered word, and off goes <var 29 EA02 /var> on a grand adventure! What wonders await at journey's end?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_PIXIE_1<tab>Carried by the wind, the leaf flutters to the ground─and so does <var 29 EA02 /var> return to your side. Was the journey a fruitful one?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_PIXIE_1<tab>Carried by the wind, the leaf flutters to the ground─and so does <var 29 EA02 /var> return to your side. Was the journey a fruitful one?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_PIXIE_1<tab>You have no more need of <var 29 EA02 /var>? So be it! I shall steal quietly from your loyal servant's dreams.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_PIXIE_1<tab>You have no more need of <var 29 EA02 /var>? So be it! I shall steal quietly from your loyal servant's dreams.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_PIXIE_1<tab>Very well. I shall slip quietly from <var 29 EA02 /var>'s dreams. May your leaf flutter, float, and find a way back to you.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_PIXIE_1<tab>Very well. I shall slip quietly from <var 29 EA02 /var>'s dreams. May your leaf flutter, float, and find a way back to you.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_EQUIP_PIXIE_1<tab>From verdant green to glittering gold, so does the leaf take on delightful hues with each new season. If you would see <var 29 EA02 /var> dressed in new colors, your beautiful branch will attend to the task.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_EQUIP_PIXIE_1<tab>From verdant green to glittering gold, so does the leaf take on delightful hues with each new season. If you would see <var 29 EA02 /var> dressed in new colors, your beautiful branch will attend to the task.
